{"tid":1590280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非行動]寫信，Letter to the world","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:51:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T17:01:54.000Z","uid":202895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"562163aadd464e69d618c5977979e7986f3a4407","tid":1590280,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:51:15.000Z","msg":"有人話我地文宣攻勢差咗，<br />\n我就諗起之前有一個Post係講寄信去中國，傳播革命思想<br />\n咁我呢個傻仔就突然認為可以試下嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係可以試下擴大一下範圍，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個叫Letter to the world活動</span></strong><br />\n好似漂流瓶呢種方式咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n活動內容：寫信<br />\n<br />\n題目：反送中活動至今已超過100天，為把心聲傳到世界各地的人民手中。試以香港人的名義，撰寫信件一封，先說明反送中活動的內容，再以香港人的身份角度抒發個人感受，並舉出為何他們應支持我們的原因，加以論證，最後，建議他們支持我們的方法（如杯葛當地共匪公司，如有當地聲援活動，則需提及。）<br />\n<br />\n文體：不限（抒情/說明均可）<br />\n<br />\n語言：不限<br />\n<br />\n地點：不限（隨機派送）<br />\n<br />\n頻率：建議一日一封（昐望能持久發展，而熱情亦可保持）<br />\n<br />\n其他：<br />\n*書信結尾請呼籲佢地若收到，請去twitter Post收到嘅照片同 hashtag#LetterfromHK，睇下可唔可以相認。<br />\n<br />\n*寄信時可以hashtag#Lettertotheworld，以便統計人數及造勢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>***本次測驗不容許抄襲，copy template等等作弊手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，書信貴在溫度，原創性，可以抄自己，但唔好copy報章，他人原創等。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人想了解香港人心聲更多，而唔係新聞內容，所以儘量講多小小個人感受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔知道會唔會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，會唔會有人響應，但係我地唔做係永遠唔會成功。<br />\n呢個活動亦都係提供一D危險性低嘅活動比老人家，小朋友參加。<br />\n<br />\n最後，光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"a82621818b76479fd7ca377fff1d836d9a3c7b6e","tid":1590280,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"b1e45d139d9ec63d136f30c40eec73d3810ec57a","tid":1590280,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:52:24.000Z","msg":"唔錯<br />\n<br />\nPush推Pish<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要你<span style=\"color: gold;\">支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：提升港人身份認同<br />\n建議：各有各做<br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化民主陣營勢力<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、傳播思想、滲透內部<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n衛城革命,生活抗爭；拖垮邪惡,打倒腐敗<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n每日任務：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.幫襯良心商店、抵制送中商戶4.開AC玩國際戰線 (Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit)5.多發佈正面資訊、冷處理負面POST6.十點咆哮發泄7.訓覺前思考思考思考下，各有各做<br />\n每星期任務：1. 低消費、高儲蓄、罷買日2. 教育家中兩老3. 去連儂牆幫手<br />\n每月任務：1. 換美金，走資2. 陪審員/派傳單/放映會/各有各做<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0objsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=3a08dda7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n理非可以做的事<a href=\"https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTakeActionWithYou&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0objsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=6c6505bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TakeActionWithYou</a><br />\n良心與無良商戶<a href=\"https://www.wordsofmouth.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wordsofmouth.net%2F&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0objsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=42577418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wordsofmouth.net/</a><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\nVersion 2019.09.24"},{"pid":"61218992562cf7b2abc9c9fae33520a5bc18c718","tid":1590280,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:52:53.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8c57c3ff4f6679ecc8854a77bc537675e86a6800","tid":1590280,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28f3fd67635301bf37a63bf7be70b18ddde7bf32","tid":1590280,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:37.000Z","msg":"咁呢樣野係人人可以參與嘅，<br />\n雖然係膠膠D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係我認為幾老小少咸宜嘅活動黎"},{"pid":"5c2d141bccb80ac06ddffa4427a4b048560c3b48","tid":1590280,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁呢樣野係人人可以參與嘅，<br />\n雖然係膠膠D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係我認為幾老少咸宜嘅活動黎</blockquote><br />\n又打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> but自推"},{"pid":"503bcf9ec4cfacaf19217a94a1462f546a1e7b58","tid":1590280,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:56:05.000Z","msg":"咁大家認真咁寫一封信之後，就可以日日印日日寄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c3e3dba2110e4405718d72856559706940a8a1","tid":1590280,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"咁寫完亦可以附送靚靚文宣或者pepe<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6hNJzfG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6hNJzfG.jpg&h=52a5b1e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63023b924333b3257a8883308f49f2542a6